# Credentials for vocs AI search (Cloudflare Workers AI embeddings + reranker).
#
# The API token needs the "Workers AI" permission. These are read at:
#   - build time  -> to embed pages into the static vector store
#   - runtime     -> to embed each search query (/api/search)
#
# Generate/refresh the index locally with: pnpm --filter site exec vocs embeddings generate
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
